@bhall-ctre to provide context, our goal is to independently set the robot's forward direction regardless of its orientation upon placement on the field, which may or may not be an actual field. Using code adapted from the MAXSwerve template and incorporating a NavX gyro, we initially attempted to align the gyro's direction similarly but later decided not to interact with the gyro if it presents problems.

We hypothesized that a reset followed by a tare might suffice but are now uncertain if this approach is appropriate.

In brief, we seek guidance on the best method to achieve our objectives using your system. Thank you!
